// InterestSection.astro — "The First Test" gauge / info section
---

<section class="section" id="gauge">
  <p class="section-label">The First Test</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">Interest first.<br /><em>Then the first meeting.</em></h2>
  <p class="section-body">
    The first goal is simple: build a direct list of people who want to see Spotsylvania RFC happen.
    Social media attention helps, but a founding list gives organizers a practical way to plan the
    first interest meeting, identify possible players, find coaches and volunteers, and start
    conversations with sponsors.
  </p>

  <div class="interest-note">
    <div>
      <h3>Who should join the list?</h3>
      <p>
        Prospective players, parents, coaches, referees, volunteers, athletic trainers, local
        businesses, and anyone who wants to support rugby in Spotsylvania.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3>What happens next?</h3>
      <p>
        No commitment is required. Your response helps determine whether there is enough interest to
        schedule an interest meeting, organize early training, and shape the club's first season.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
